<text>[[Callista (given name)|Callista]], also spelled Calista, Callistee, Kallista, Kalista and Kallistee, comes from the Greek for &quot;most beautiful (feminine)&quot; (καλλίστη – &quot;kallístē&quot;).
Callista may refer to:


==Nature==
* &quot;Callista&quot; (bivalve), a genus of bivalves
