* &quot;Callista&quot; , a synonym of &quot;Erica&quot;, a heath or heather genus

==Entertainment==
* A &quot;SWAT Kats: The Radical Squadron&quot; character, the presumed ancestor of Deputy Mayor Callie Briggs
* &quot;Callista&quot; (novel), 1855 novel by John Henry Newman
